\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

,即商式是
\begin_inset Formula $Ax^{2}+Bx+C$
\end_inset

,佘式
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

,是代入(1)就可得到一个恒等式
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
centerline{
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $2x^{3}-x^{2}+5x+6=(x+2)\big(Ax^{2}+Bx+C\big)+D$
