\begin_layout 解*
设商式
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+mx+n$
\end_inset

,那末
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $x^{4}+5x^{3}+11x^{2}+ax+b=\big(x^{2}-2x+1\big)\big(x^{2}+mx+n\big)$
